data.description: Price Reduction** RARE FIND- FULLY Furnished** Available in Highly sought after Chatham Place Subdivision. A Beautiful Fully Furnished Home Close and Convenient to Shopping, Hospital and GSU. Only 5 years old and "like New". Meticulously kept. The 2-story "Williamsburg" by Keystone features 2680 Sq. Ft. of living space with 5 beds, 3 bath and upstairs laundry. Owner's suite includes dual vanities separate shower and garden tub w/tile surround, separate water closet, oil rubbed bronze fixtures, framed mirrors and 2 walk-in closets. Master Bedroom is HUGE! 3 more bedrooms upstairs and Full Bath. Downstairs features a guest room and full bath plus a large family room, Formal dining room, spacious kitchen with walk-in pantry, white cabinets, and stainless-steel Whirlpool appliances, breakfast bar with pendant lighting and Breakfast area. Enjoy LVT flooring in all living areas downstairs, 9' ceilings up and down, 2-car side entry garage with auto-opener and fully sodded front and side yard with irrigation and Landscaping. Large Covered Back Patio. Backyard is a Private Oasis with Large Firepit and fully Fenced with outdoor furnishing including a BBQ pit stays with home. Quality Builders Transferrable Limited Warranty included. A Must see. Call today for an appointment and move in before the Holidays.
